data.description: Quietly Nestle in Gilbert Estates on a large lot. This spacious 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths, with a 3 car garage home has everything your family needs. Upon entry there is a bedroom on the left and right with a full bath also on the right. With an open concept floor plan. The spacious living room has an electrical fireplace, wood mantle and warm colored brick. The eat in kitchen features a BREAKFAST BAR, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, CENTER ISLAND, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, and large walk in PANTRY. Minor bedrooms three and four are roomy and located on the right side of the home, with another full bath to share. The relaxing primary bedroom is located on the left side of the home, perfect for anyone looking for some PRIVACY. The primary ensuite bathroom has a STAND ALONE SHOWER, GARDEN TUB, HIS & HER SINKS, and a LARGE WALK-IN CLOSET. Another feature is SOLAR PANELS to save on your energy bills and WATER SOFTENER SYSTEM. A covered back patio. A nice size backyard for your family, friends and fur babies to enjoy. Don't wait, call us for your private showing!!
